INSERT INTO realtime.position (
                        vehicle_id,
                        mta_id,
                        stop_id,
                        status,
                        bearing,
                        geom,
                        recorded_at
                    )
                    SELECT
                        unnest($1::text[]),
                        unnest($2::text[]),
                        unnest($3::int[]),
                        unnest($4::text[]),
                        unnest($5::real[]),
                        ST_SetSRID(unnest($6::geometry[]), 4326),
                        unnest($7::timestamptz[])
